@startuml
title Chapter 3.02 - Adapter Pattern Class Model

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam linetype polyline
top to bottom direction

together {
  class GasMixer {
    +mixerGas()
  }

  class GasDisplay {
    +displayGas()
  }
}

interface iO2Sensor {
  +instance : void*
  +gimmeO2Flow(instance) : int
  +gimmeO2Conc(instance) : int
  +destroy(instance)
}

class O2SensorFactory {
  +Create(vendor) : iO2Sensor*
}

together {
class AcmeO2Adapter {
  +sensor : iO2Sensor
  +itsAcmeO2SensorProxy : AcmeO2SensorProxy*
  --
  +gimmeO2Flow(instance) : int
  +gimmeO2Conc(instance) : int
  +destroy(instance)
}

class UltimateO2Adapter {
  +sensor : iO2Sensor
  +itsUltimateO2SensorProxy : UltimateO2SensorProxy*
  --
  +gimmeO2Flow(instance) : int
  +gimmeO2Conc(instance) : int
  +destroy(instance)
}
}

together {
  class AcmeO2SensorProxy {
    +getO2Conc() : unsigned int
    +getO2Flow() : unsigned long
  }

  class UltimateO2SensorProxy {
    +accessO2Conc() : unsigned int
    +accessGasFlow() : unsigned long
  }
}

class main {
  +main(argc, argv)
}

main -down-> GasDisplay : calls
main -down-> GasMixer : calls

GasDisplay -up..> iO2Sensor : uses target API
GasMixer -up..> iO2Sensor : uses target API
GasDisplay ..> O2SensorFactory : requests sensor
GasMixer ..> O2SensorFactory : requests sensor

O2SensorFactory -down..> AcmeO2Adapter : creates
O2SensorFactory -down..> UltimateO2Adapter : creates

AcmeO2Adapter -up..|> iO2Sensor
UltimateO2Adapter -up..|> iO2Sensor

AcmeO2Adapter *-down- AcmeO2SensorProxy : adapts
UltimateO2Adapter *-down- UltimateO2SensorProxy : adapts

note right of iO2Sensor
Target interface expected by
client-side code.
end note

note right of O2SensorFactory
Factory hides concrete adapter
selection from clients.
end note

note right of AcmeO2Adapter
Converts Acme sensor API
to iO2Sensor operations.
end note

note right of UltimateO2Adapter
Converts Ultimate sensor API
to iO2Sensor operations and
applies unit conversion.
end note

@enduml
